videos.description: Garrison Brooks steals an inbound pass allowing Sterling Manley to bank in the shot for North Carolina.
videos.headline: UNC turns steal into Manley bucket

videos.description: North Carolina uses some nice passing to setup a one-handed jam for Cameron Johnson.
videos.headline: Good ball movement leads to Johnson dunk

videos.description: Pittsburgh's offensive rebound leads to Marcus Carr draining a shot from way downtown as the shot clock expires.
videos.headline: Carr hits deep-3 pointer to beat shot clock

videos.description: Luke Maye's great feed allows Christian Johnson to score on the fast break plus a foul for North Carolina.
videos.headline: Maye nice transition pass leads to Johnson and-1 layup

videos.description: Joel Berry II misses a 3-pointer but Garrison Brooks grabs the rebound to score plus a foul for North Carolina,
videos.headline: Brooks scores and-1 after getting offensive board

videos.description: North Carolina's Theo Pinson hammers down a big dunk with one hand off a missed shot.
videos.headline: Pinson rattles the rim with putback dunk

videos.description: Theo Pinson throws a perfect pass down court to Kenny Williams who scores on the fast break for the Tar Heels.
videos.headline: Pinson's great outlet pass leads to Williams' lay-in
